OL,3,CHeathrow chief has 'extra loud phone'
OL,4,Cafter sleeping while fire unfolded
OL,6,FA Heathrow-commissioned inquiry led by
OL,7,Fformer transport secretary Ruth Kelly
OL,8,Ffound Mr Woldbye was not woken by
OL,9,Falerts sent to his mobile, which was
OL,10,Fon a bedside table, because it had
OL,11,Fgone into silent mode "without him
OL,12,Fbeing aware".
OL,14,FAsked at the Airlines 2025 event in
OL,15,FWestminster if he had since obtained
OL,16,Fan "extra loud phone", Mr Woldbye
OL,17,Freplied: "Oh, absolutely. And more."
OL,19,FHe said he was "personally devastated"
OL,20,Fby his phone being on silent,
OL,21,Fdescribing it as a "technical glitch".
