OL,3,CHeathrow chief has 'extra loud phone'
OL,4,Cafter sleeping while fire unfolded
OL,6,FBut he added that "nothing in this
OL,7,Fworld should be depending on me alone"
OL,8,Fand "all the right people were there
OL,9,Fto take the right decisions".
OL,11,FMore than 270,000 air passenger
OL,12,Fjourneys were disrupted by the
OL,13,Fincident.
OL,15,FMr Woldbye said businesses "need to be
OL,16,Fable to trust our utilities", and we
OL,17,Fare "not in a country where everybody
OL,18,Fneeds a back-up".
